  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of the cognitive-behavioral
      treatment program CANDIS among n=450 patients with cannabis use disorders in a mulicenter
      randomized-controlled clinical trial (n=11 outpatient treatment centers).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
